{"article_id":"PEJiqy2hEWaJj9kP","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"A new analysis from Washington Post Beijing bureau chief Anna Fifield suggests","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"that the real number of people","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"who have died from the coronavirus in Wuhan , China ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"where the virus originated ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"is more than 16 times higher than the number","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"reported by communist China .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"The coronavirus pandemic","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"ravaging the globe","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"officially claimed 2,563 lives in Wuhan ,","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"where it began in a market","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"that sold exotic animals for consumption .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"But evidence","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"emerging from the city","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"as it stirs from its two-month hibernation","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"suggests","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"the real death toll is exponentially higher . ...","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"Using photos","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"posted online ,","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"social media sleuths have estimated","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"that Wuhan funeral homes had returned 3,500 urns a day since March 23 .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"That would imply a death toll in Wuhan of about 42,000","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"- or 16 times the official number .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Another widely shared calculation ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"based on Wuhan ' s 84 furnaces","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"running nonstop","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"and each cremation taking an hour ,","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"put the death toll at 46,800 .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"The analysis from The Washington Post comes","depth":4},{"id":28,"text":"after Bloomberg News reported this week","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"that U.S. intelligence officials have presented President Donald Trump with a highly classified report","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"that confirmed","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"that China lied about the extent of the outbreak .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"\" China ' s public reporting on cases and deaths is intentionally incomplete , \"","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"Bloomberg News reported ,","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"according to three U.S. officials","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"that it spoke to .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"\" Two of the officials said","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"the report concludes","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"that China ' s numbers are fake . \"","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"Vice President Mike Pence told CNN this week :","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"\" The reality is that we could have been better off","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"if China had been more forthcoming .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"What appears evident now is that","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"long before the world learned in December","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"that China was dealing with this ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"and maybe as much as a month earlier than that ,","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"that the outbreak was real in China . \"","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"White House Coronavirus Response Coordinator Dr. Deborah Birx also indicated this week","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"that China ' s lying about the extent of the outbreak harmed the rest of the world .","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"\" When you talk about could we have known something different ,","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"you know ,","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"I think","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"all of us ,","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"I was overseas","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"when this happened in Africa","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"and I think","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"when you look at the China data originally ,","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"and you said ,","depth":14},{"id":58,"text":"there ' s 80 million people , or 20 million people in Wuhan and 80 million people in Hubei ,","depth":14},{"id":59,"text":"and they come up with the number of 50,000 ,","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"you start thinking of this more like SARS","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"than you do this kind of global pandemic , \"","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"Birx said .","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"Birx said","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"when U.S. officials looked at the data from China during the first days of the outbreak","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"that she did not think","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"that it would be a global pandemic","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"based on the data","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"that China provided .","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"\" So , I think","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"the medical community interpreted the Chinese data","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"as this was serious ,","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"but smaller","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"than anyone expected","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"because I think","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"probably we were missing a significant amount of the data \" from China ,","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"Birx added .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"Communist China also has a history","depth":3},{"id":79,"text":"of lying about epidemic outbreaks","depth":4},{"id":80,"text":"that originate within its borders .","depth":4},{"id":81,"text":"The New York Times reported on the SARS outbreak in April 2003 :","depth":3},{"id":82,"text":"In a rare public admission of failure , if not deception , the Chinese government disclosed today","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"that cases of a dangerous new respiratory disease were many times higher","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"than previously reported ,","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"and stripped two top officials of their power . ...","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"Admitting to the existence of more than 200 previously undisclosed SARS patients in military hospitals ,","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"the official , Deputy Health Minister Gao Qiang , said","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"that as of Friday Beijing had 339 confirmed cases of SARS and an additional 402 suspected cases .","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"Ten days ago , Health Minister Zhang Wenkang said","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"there were only 22 confirmed SARS cases in Beijing .","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"Last Wednesday , the World Health Organization caused a stir here","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"by estimating","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"that there could be as many as 100 to 200 cases .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":187,"left":171,"right":186,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":120,"right":170,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":99,"right":119,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":0,"right":98,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":98,"left":96,"right":97,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":96,"left":1,"right":95,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":103,"right":118,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":103,"left":100,"right":102,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":100,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":8,"right":101,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":107,"right":117,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":106,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":106,"left":105,"right":14,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":105,"left":11,"right":104,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":112,"right":116,"relation":"j